cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with image colorization using deep learning techniques. The paper also involves the use of convolutional neural networks (cs.LG) and machine learning algorithms (cs.AI) for colorization. Additionally, the paper mentions the possibility of extending the approach to video colorization (cs.MM) and proposes an image retrieval algorithm (cs.GR) for selecting reference images.
